-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:opacity-90\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold-light), var(--color-gold))\">Proposer un projet</button></a><a href=\"/projets\"><button class=\"w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-[12px] md:text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white/70 hover:border-gold/40 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300\">Voir les opportunités</button></a></div><div class=\"mt-16 md:mt-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-8 gap-x-6 md:gap-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-10 w-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">120+</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 text-center\">Projets financés</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">4,2 Mrd</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 text-center\">FCFA investis</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">18%</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 text-center\">Rendement moyen</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">98%</span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 text-center\">Taux de satisfaction</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center mb-16\"><span class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gold/60 mb-4\">Opportunités sélectionnées</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">Projets en vedette</h2>