duits agricoles transformés vers l&#x27;Europe.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><span>Voir le projet</span><span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\">→</span></div></div></div></a><a class=\"group block\" href=\"/projets/project2\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-gold/20 transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"relative h-52 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Énergie Solaire Sahel\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project2.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-3 right-3 bg-gold/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gold/30 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">+22%<!-- --> / an</div><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Énergie</div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Énergie Solaire Sahel</h3><p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">Installation de micro-centrales solaires dans les zones rurales du nord Bénin.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><span>Voir le projet</span><span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\">→</span></div></div></div></a><a class=\"group block\" href=\"/projets/project3\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-gold/20 transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"relative h-52 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Logistique Côtière\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fgenerated-project3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-3 right-3 bg-gold/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gold/30 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">+15%<!-- --> / an</div><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Transport</div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Logistique Côtière</h3><p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">Modernisation des infrastructures portuaires pour fluidifier le commerce régional en Afrique de l&#x27;Ouest.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\"><span>Voir le projet</span><span class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\">→</span></div></div></div></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 px-4 md:px-6 border-t border-white/[0.04]\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20 items-center\"><div><span class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gold/60\">Notre protocole</span><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">Un audit<!-- --> <span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-gold-glow), var(--color-gold))\">rigoureux</span><br/>à chaque étape</h2><div class=\"mt-10 space-y-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-gold/50\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">01</span><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Sécurité des actifs</h4><p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Standards bancaires pour la protection de vos données et le suivi des transactions financières.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-gold/50\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">02</span><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Expertise locale</h4><p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Nos analystes basés au Bénin évaluent la pertinence de chaque projet sur le marché ouest-africain.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-gold/50\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">03</span><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Transparence totale</h4><p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Chaque investisseur dispose d&#x27;un tableau de bord pour suivre en temps réel l&#x27;évolution de ses placements.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative mt-12 lg:mt-0\"><div class=\"absolute -inset-4 rounded-3xl bg-gold/[0.03] border border-gold/5\"></div><div class=\"relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-surface\"><svg width=\"40\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 40 30\" fill=\"none\" class=\"mb-6 opacity-30\"><path d=\"M0 30V18C0 8 6 2 18 0l2 4C12 6 9 10 9 14h9v16H0zm22 0V18C22 8 28 2 40 0l2 4C34 6 31 10 31 14h9v16H22z\" fill=\"var(--color-gold)\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-white text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, serif\">Bâtir un écosystème où le capital rencontre l&#x27;innovation pour transformer durablement l&#x27;économie du continent africain.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-px bg-gold/50\"></div><span class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gold/50\">Notre Vision</span></div></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 pt-28 pb-14 px-6 font-sans relative\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[200px] bg-gold/10 blur-[140px] pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-20\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 border-2 border-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gold text-lg\">G</div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Golden <span class=\"text-gold\">Invest</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs\"